  lines:
  - portrait: {fileID: 0}
    isLeftSide: 0
    text: "Sen de mi her \u015Feyin y\u0131k\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131 izliyorsun?"
  - portrait: {fileID: 0}
    isLeftSide: 1
    text: "Bazen y\u0131k\u0131m, yeniden kurman\u0131n tek yolu."
  - portrait: {fileID: 0}
    isLeftSide: 0
    text: "Demek anl\u0131yorsun... \u0130\xE7indeki ate\u015Fi hissediyorum."
